{"by":"gitowiec","id":47778393,"kids":[47779088],"parent":47776557,"text":"The most important thing about sleep I learned is to fall asleep at the same moment of every day. Make it 22:00 or 23:00 or 00:00. Whatever is comfortable for you. But you have to stick to the chosen hour as hard as you can. Every day from now on it has to be that hour. After you get used to that you will notice a much better effect of the sleep.","time":1776258041,"type":"comment"}